g.aria-label: spi_done = '1' and powered_up_reg = '0' and index_reg = 2 / index_reg* ← 0 powered_up_reg* ← '1'
timer_reg = TIMER_MAX and powered_up_reg = '1' / timer_reg* ← 0 irq_o ← '1'
spi_done = '1' and powered_up_reg = '1' and index_reg = 9 / index_reg* ← 0
spi_done = '1' and (powered_up_reg = '0' and index_reg < 2 or powered_up_reg = '1' and index_reg < 9) / index_reg* ← index_reg + 1
timer_reg = TIMER_MAX and powered_up_reg = '0' / timer_reg* ← 0 irq_o ← '0'
